"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-noah-lyles-painted-nails-olympics-b2588417.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The Independent's journalism is supported by our readers.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.802147042403564e-39, \"text\": \"The Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn commission.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am a person who knows that a lot of people have different opinions and they have them for different reasons,' he says  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  OlympianNoah Lyleshas brushed off the criticism he's faced for having hisnailspainted.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team USA track and field star addressed the online critcism he faced after the Olympics' Opening Ceremony during an interview withUS Weekly, published on July 30.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When hefirst arrived in Paris last week, Lyles had his nails painted white, with the word \\\"ICON\\\" written in blue polish across his nails.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 851, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999911640316, \"rank\": 8.83595955345368e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9583014105128251, \"rank\": 0.0375019476685246, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On social media, the look divided viewers, with one alleging that painted nails were meant for women.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Lyles said that he's not letting the criticism get to him, since he does not take the comments too seriously.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9583014105128251, \"rank\": 0.0375019476685246, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a person who knows that a lot of people have different opinions and they have them for different reasons,\\\" he toldUS Weekly.\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be honest, I am so confident in myself that it does not really matter.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's funny at times.\\\"\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He acknowledged that while he has an understanding for a difference in opinions, he finds amusement in how people on social media get so upset over some decisions he makes.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes, it's like: 'Hey, I know you were brought up this way, but I was brought up that way,' and the fact that you can not see the differences of why I might do it, I find that entertaining,\\\" he continued.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know, peoplelikeme because I do this.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just being myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The US sprinter also spoke candidly about his personality, and how sometimes he's perceived in a negative light because of his confidence.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1883, \"end\": 1885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9929396313192915, \"rank\": 0.0065557524969652985, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The most misunderstood thing is the balance between cocky and confident,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a strong line that people assume my confidence is cockiness.\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will say this.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anybody who thought I was cocky and met me, they are instantly like: 'Oh, that's the nicest, coolest guy I have ever met in my life.'\\\"\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He further described how people's opinions of him change once they get to know him.\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never blame anybody who thinks that I am cocky.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just a 'you have not met me situation.'\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's all,\\\" he concluded.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics is not Lyles' first time showcasing his painted nails.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2567, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9583014105128251, \"rank\": 0.0375019476685246, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the New Balance Indoor Grand Prix in February, he had his nails painted red and black, and also shared a photo of his hands over his face after competing in the event on social media.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISU_Grand_Prix_of_Figure_Skating\", \"score\": 0.988769464653553, \"rank\": 0.008995238825775754, \"text\": \"Grand Prix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISU_Grand_Prix_of_Figure_Skating\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISU_Grand_Prix_of_Figure_Skating\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have waited and worked for eight years to see the numbers I have produced this year in the 60m.\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so glad it's finally here,\\\" he wrote in the caption of his poston Xat the time.\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles also had hisnails painted white in June, after he won two gold medals at the US Olympic track and field trials.\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 3105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3071, \"end\": 3073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9929396313192915, \"rank\": 0.0065557524969652985, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3158, \"end\": 3169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0703768733260903e-19, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"